name: "Even if it's contrary to the Sun" by Cinthia Ponce
description:
I don't know what to do, am I living the right way?
I don't have to know where to go or if. The doubt kills me.
I think I was in yesterday or at least that's what I feel.
Why is everyone walking so fast?
I'm going to keep going, even if it's contrary to the Sun.

Intervention, customization and collage of images. Conceptual art.
